      "rationale": "At the nominal operating point, CFD inlet velocity profile was matched to the experimental pump inlet using a developed pipe-flow profile at the measured flow rate. Outlet pressure was set to match the measured differential head within 1.2%. At off-design operating points, boundary conditions were set by linear interpolation from the nominal condition without experimental confirmation of equivalency. The validity of this interpolation for the non-linear hemolysis response is unverified. Achieved level 2."
